    "body" : "<p><code>-locale</code> is still supported, but it’s currently ignored in newer JDKs (known bug JDK-8222793).<br />\nTo force English output, use JVM options instead:</p>\n<pre><code>javadoc -J-Duser.language=en -J-Duser.country=US ...\n</code></pre>\n",
